summary.label:
PixelWave is an experimental wavetable synth with old school pixel interface.

Key features:
 • it is possible to draw waveform and play it at the same time;
 • export to WAV;
 • nine predefined waveforms;
 • changeable number of octaves (from 2 to 6);
 • MIDI keyboard support;
 • Audiobus and IAA support.
